- A header, with your name in it! *** 

- A home page, with a row of images 

- A “Contact” page, linked to from the home page ***
	o Your contact page should include an HTML5 form for contacting you ***

- Somewhere on the site:
	o A block quote 
	o An ordered list 
	o At least 1 external link 
	o At least 3 different CSS selectors. ***

- Add a background image or color and alter its opacity. *** 

- Import an external font and use it to change your name in the header. ***

- Pretty up your home page’s row of images by using at least 2 different CSS3 effects. 
	o Examples might be border-image, box-shadow, or border-radius 

- Style your contact form & submit button on your “Contact” page 

- Put your whole project on Github